description.narrative:
(1) Prepared and updated national GHG inventory (2000-2012); 

(2) Prepared reports on the impacts, vulnerability and adaptation measures to address climate change, variabiilty and extreme events, 
(3) Prepared a report on GHG mitigation policies and measures to address climate change; 

(4) Prepared a report on the description of national circumstances and other relevant information. 

(5) Publication of the Third National Communication (TNC) and Biennial Update Report (BUR) documents.

comment.narrative:
(1) Indonesia submitted Initial National Communication (INC) document to UNFCCC in 1999;
(2) Indonesia submitted the Second National Communication (SNC) in 2010, 
(3) These two documents made significant contribution in building up capacity in the country to prepare future documents.
